quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  39,75,"Nden √Ďalnde, a yi'ay Malaa'ika'en no fiiltii Arsi ki, hi…ďe senina yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, e huunde ko heefer…ďe wi'ata Mo, kon ko haananaa Mo. Allah √Īaawira nun…óal, hakkunde tageefo ngon fow: O teddina Mo muuyanaa…ďe …ďen, O lepte leptee…ďe …ďen. Ontuma wi'ee: Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tageefo ngon, e fii ko O √Īaawiri kon yurmeende, hakkunde jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, O heertinani yurmeende Makko nden, muumini'en, yeddu…ďe …ďen hanndi e lepte …óen."
  40,1,"Haa, Miim: yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yewtanooma ka simoore Al Baqarah."
  40,2,"Jippinde Quraana ummaade e Alla Teddu…óo O hay gooto foolataa Mbo ganndu…óo maslahaaji jiyaa…ďe Makko e dow Nelaa…óo Makko."
  40,3,"Haforoowo junubaaji …óin, Ja…ďanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Sa…ótu…óo leptugol salii…óo tuubannde Mo, Jom neema yaaju…óo. Rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko tun, ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden, √Ďalnde Darngal. O yo…ďa …ďe, ko …ďe hanndi kon."
  40,4,"Alaa ko wennjata e Aayeeje Allah …ďanngin…óe tawhiidi e goonga Nulaa…ďe …ďen, si wanaa yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen, sabu jii…ďagol haqille ma…ď…ďe. Wata a sunor hoditoraa, ko …ďe woni dillirde jawle e neemaaji. Ko …ďe nennitiranaa, ko hebilangol …ďe fewjana …ďe."
  40,5,"Ado …ďee …óoo, hari yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen fenniino Nulaa…ďe mun, feddeeji …óin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe kadi fenni Aadi, e Samuuda, e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen, e wonndii…ďe Madyana …ďen e Fir'awna'en fow. Mofte kala e …ďen …óon, himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun on, fii warugol mo. ∆Āe wennjiri meere ma…ď…ďe, fii bonnitirgol nde goonga kan. Kono Mi nanngi …ďe. Tesko no nanngal Am wa…ótinirnoo e ma…ď…ďe. ∆äum ko lepte sa…ótu…óe wonunoo."
  40,6,"Ko wano Allah √Īaawiri non fii halkugol …óen mofte fennunoo…ďe Nulaa…ďe mun, Konngol Joomi maa ngol, an Nulaa…óo, jojjiri e yeddu…ďe …ďen: wonnde pellet, ko …ďe yim…ďe Yiite."
  40,7,"Malaa'ikaa…ďe ronndii…ďe Arsi Joomi maa kin, an Nulaa…óo, e …ďeya won…ďe sera makki, hi…ďe la…ď…ďina Joomi ma…ď…ďe, e kon ko hanndaa e Makko, …ďe gom…óina Mo, …ďe …óa…ď…ďira Mo, haforangol gom…óim…ďe Allah …ďen, …ďe wi'a: Joomi amen, ganndal Maa ngal e yurmeende Maa nden, yaajanii kala huunde. Yawtan tuubu…ďe …ďen, junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďen jokku…ďe diina Maa kan, da…óndaa …ďe kadi, Yiite ngen."